# Config Safety

- `damage_classes` must stay `[no_damage, minor_damage, major_damage, destroyed]` unless the user explicitly requests a change. Changing this breaks the model, dataset, evaluation, and dashboard.
- `train_split + val_split + test_split` must sum to 1.0.
- `image_size`, `crop_padding_pixels`, `min_building_area_pixels` must be positive integers.
- `subset_strategy` must remain `event_aware` to prevent data leakage.
- When adding new config keys, update `docs/interface_contracts.md` if they affect module boundaries.
- Paths must be relative to the project root, never absolute.
